                    <p class="text-slate-600">Confira a experiência de quem já conta com a proteção Premium Clube.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-slate-100 italic">
                        <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4"><i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i></div>
